{
  "texts": [
    "Yasunaga et al.",
    "retrieve relevant nodes and create a joint graph that includes the QA context and the relevant nodes.",
    "Kang et al. and Kim et al.",
    "focus on retrieving triples rather than individual nodes and edges to capture more complex relational data.",
    "Particularly, some retrieval problems can be solved by reasoning chains, which can be simplified to retrieve the path between the question and the target entity (Lo and Lim, 2023; Choudhary and Reddy, 2023)."
  ]
}